(19, 1, '2017-12-02 04:34:49', '2017-12-02 04:34:49', '<section class="about-us new-patient">\r\n<div class="container">\r\n<div class="row">\r\n<div class="col-md-8 col-sm-8">\r\n<h2>New Patients</h2>\r\nPHR Laser Centers was the first company in Michigan to offer laser technology for permanent hair removal. We pride ourselves in making our patients feel confident and satisfied with definite results in achieving smooth, beautiful skin anywhere on the face and body. Our lasers treat all skin tones and our technicians decades of experience. PHR Centers has been serving Michigan since 1981.\r\nOn average patients require four to six treatments, treating once every 8 to 10 weeks as our body produces hair over a 12 to 15 month period of time. You will experience approximately two months with no hair in-between your treatments. One or two weeks prior to your next cycle treatment you will start to notice new, finer hair growth. We always re-evaluate each patient at a fourth cycle treatment and determine if further treatments are needed or desired.\r\n\r\nOur monthly specials and promotions vary from month to month. PHR Laser Centers does not require pre-pay packages. We offer a pay per treatment option and additional discounts if three or more areas are treated simultaneously.\r\n\r\nAppointments can be scheduled for you within 24 to 48 hours. If you would like to schedule an appointment for your complimentary consultation, quote and test spot, please call the office. Appointments may also be scheduled via e-mail, if that is more convenient for you. Please advise us if you are presently taking any photosensitive medication or using any photosensitive topical lotion or cream, as patients must be off both for 7 days prior to any laser treatment. Also, if you are tweezing or waxing, it is best to stop and clip or shave the hair, but please leave us two days of hair growth prior initial consultation to evaluate the areas. You will need to closely shave the area before your full treatment.\r\n\r\nPlease feel free to contact us to schedule your appointment. We look forward to hearing from you!\r\n\r\n<a class="btn btn-primary" href="http://webdesigndemo1.com/phr-centers/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/Hair-Removal-Client-Brochure-Vectus.pdf">DOWNLOAD YOUR BROCHOURE</a>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="col-md-4 col-sm-4">\r\n<div class="request-form">\r\n	<h3>Request A FREE Consultation!</h3>\r\n[contact-form-7 id="90" title="contact us"]</div>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>', 'New Patients', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'new-patients', '', '', '2017-12-20 11:27:01', '2017-12-20 11:27:01', '', 0, 'http://webdesigndemo1.com/phr-centers/?page_id=19', 0, 'page', '', 0),
