(52, 1, '2017-12-02 06:57:21', '2017-12-02 06:57:21', '<div class="row">\r\n<div class="col-md-12">\r\n<h2>LASER HAIR REMOVAL</h2>\r\n<img class="img-right" src="http://webdesigndemo1.com/phr-centers/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/laser-removal.jpg" />Laser hair removal is one of the most common cosmetic procedures in the U.S. Laser Hair Removal is the proven method for permanent hair removal on any and all areas of the body. Using specialized equipment under the care of our trained specialists, the individual hair follicles are targeted to prevent hair re-growth. Laser hair removal is a safe, fast and effective alternative for dealing with unwanted hair on any part of the body including the face, back, underarms, bikini line, legs, and arms.\r\n\r\nPHR Centers offers quick, knowledgeable, friendly service and the highest quality of care from our experienced technicians. Say good-bye to shaving, plucking, waxing, and all the harsh chemicals that can damage your skin. With just a few visits, you can say hello to the smooth, beautiful and hairless skin youve been dreaming of. We specialize in Laser hair removal for Men, Women and Children. The Vectus laser is virtually pain free, faster and results are permanent. Call our office today to schedule a complimentary consultation and speak with one of our laser hair removal professionals.\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="col-md-8">\r\n<h2>Vectus Lasers</h2>\r\nThe Vectus Laser is the intelligent choice providing the fastest and most effective treatment for unwanted hair removal. A dedicated solution for high-volume hair removal, The Vectus Laser features the integrated Skintel Melanin Reader, the only FDA cleared device, providing the safest way to optimize Laser Hair Removal treatments tailored to each client''s skin type, lifestyle, hair type and ethnicity.\r\n\r\nThe Vectus Laser features the industry''s largest Sapphire Chill tip that cools and protects the skin''s epidermis before and during treatment. Clients are comfortable throughout their treatment allowing our Laser Technicians to quickly remove unwanted hair with speed and accuracy, even on the largest areas including backs, lower legs, arms, chests and thighs. With the Vectus technology, Laser Hair Removal is completed even in these large areas in less than fitteen minutes.\r\n\r\nDownload Our Brochure\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="col-md-4">\r\n<div class="services-form">\r\n<h3>Schedule a Free Consultation</h3>\r\n[contact-form-7 id="184" title="App form"]\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<h2>F.A.Q</h2>\r\n<div class="toggle">\r\n<div class="toggle-title ">\r\n<h3><i></i><span class="title-name">How Does it work?</span></h3>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="toggle-inner">\r\n\r\nA laser produces a beam of highly concentrated light. The light is emitted through the chilled sapphire tip that is placed on the epidermis or top of skin. Using either the Vectus Diode or the LightSheer Diode, the beam of light is absorbed by the pigment or color located in hair follicles.\r\n\r\nThe laser pulses for a fraction of a second, just long enough to vaporize the pigment, disabling thousands of follicles at a time to eliminate and significantly impede the hair''s growth. LightSheerDiode Laser and the newest Laser hair removal machine called the Vectus both have a special contact-cooling hand-piece. It directs the laser energy to the hair root while protecting and cooling the surrounding skin.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="toggle">\r\n<div class="toggle-title ">\r\n<h3><i></i><span class="title-name">What does laser hair removal feel like?</span></h3>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="toggle-inner">\r\n\r\nThe laser can feel like a light pick or snap, depending on color and density of hair.The unique chill tip allows us to treat very sensitive skin and even children may have virtually pain-free laser treatments. Laser treatment itself may cause a slight tingling sensation or warming sensation. Most patients tolerate the procedure well and have no down time so they may return to their normal activities the same day.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="toggle">\r\n<div class="toggle-title ">\r\n<h3><i></i><span class="title-name">How many treatments will I need?</span></h3>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="toggle-inner">\r\n\r\nThe hair growth cycle consists of the Anagen, Catagen, and Telogen phases. Laser hair removal is most effective while hair is in the Anagen phase, when the hair is still growing and the root or papilla''s follicle is full of melanin or color. The Catagen and Telogen phases are resting or shedding periods and occur after the hair has lived its lifecycle of 8-10 weeks. Because the individual hairs of the body go through this growth cycle at separate times, each batch or cycle of hair must be treated on schedule for best results. More than one laser treatment is necessary to target every hair at the right time\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="toggle">\r\n<div class="toggle-title ">\r\n<h3><i></i><span class="title-name">How long does a session last?</span></h3>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="toggle-inner">\r\n\r\nThe length of a laser session may be a few minutes to an hour or more, depending on the size of the area being treated.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="toggle">\r\n<div class="toggle-title ">\r\n<h3><i></i><span class="title-name">What can I expect after my treatment?</span></h3>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="toggle-inner">\r\n\r\nThe appearance of the treated area immediately after a laser session will vary from patient to patient depending on the extent of treatment and skin type. Immediate after effects, if any, are minor. They may include redness and swelling, which disappear in a short time. Most people return to normal activity immediately.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="toggle">\r\n<div class="toggle-title ">\r\n<h3><i></i><span class="title-name">What type of Laser does PHR Centers use?</span></h3>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="toggle-inner">\r\n\r\nAt PHR Laser Centers, we use only proven state-of-the-art technology approved by the FDA: Vectus Laser Hair Removal by Palomar. This is the newest and the largest Diode chill- tip which can treat full legs or full backs in 15 minutes and the LightSheer Diode Laser. These systems are specially designed to permanently remove unwanted hair quickly, less painfully, and more reliably than any other laser hair removal systems.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'Laser Hair Removal', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'laser-hair-removal', '', '', '2017-12-20 11:18:14', '2017-12-20 11:18:14', '', 0, 'http://webdesigndemo1.com/phr-centers/?post_type=our_services&#038;p=52', 0, 'our_services', '', 0),
