(56, 1, '2017-12-02 06:58:14', '2017-12-02 06:58:14', '<div class="row">\r\n<div class="col-md-12">\r\n<h2>Vanquish Non-Surgical Fat Reduction at PHR LASER CENTERS</h2>\r\n<img class="img-right" src="http://webdesigndemo1.com/phr-centers/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/vanquish.jpg" />Vanquish Fat Removal is the newest state of the art, non-invasive Fat Removal and Fat Reduction procedure that eliminates unwanted belly fat using Safe RF Technology to destroy the fat cells.\r\n\r\nVanquish destroy''s those stubborn fat cells without harming the skin or surrounding muscle. This new technology allows the fat cells to melt evenly as compared to outdated cooling technology. Vanquish technology uses radio-frequency to heat the fat cells causing apoptosis (the destruction of the fat cell). The destroyed fat cells are then flushed out of the body via the lymphatic system.\r\n\r\nGet into your skinny jeans, say goodbye to your muffin top and love handles with Vanquish. Appointments can be done in as little as 30-45 minutes and scheduled on your lunch hour. Call today for a complimentary consultation and special package discounted pricing and promotions.\r\n<div class="video-area">\r\n\r\n<iframe class="video-left" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/nsmwt2kf0Dw" width="100%" height="315" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen="allowfullscreen"></iframe><strong>Vanquish Fat Removal can help you eliminate Fat.</strong>\r\n\r\nVanquish can eliminate Fat without the side effects associated with Liposuction or Gastric Bypass. This new procedure does not require anesthesia or the risk, since Vanquish is non-invasive there is no risk of infection or downtime. The Vanquish procedure takes 30-45 minutes, you can return to work immediately without interrupting your personal or professional lifestyle.\r\n\r\nOur doctors recommend 4 treatments to enjoy the maximum benefits. Lose inches in weeks, not months!\r\nVanquish has minimal side effects, these may include redness of the skin and a slight warm sensation at the treatment site, there has been no reported pain following the procedure.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="clearfix"></div>\r\n\r\n<div class="col-md-8 col-sm-12">\r\n<strong>The Vanquish Fat Removal Advantage</strong>\r\n\r\nVanquish treatments cover larger areas in half the time of Cool Sculpting technology.\r\nVanquish is less expensive than other Non-Invasive procedures.\r\nVanquish Fat Removal is <b>No-Touch</b> and <b>Non-Invasive</b> unlike other fat reduction procedures.\r\nVanquish treatments only take 30 minutes and require no restrictions or limitations before or after the procedure.\r\n<a class="btn brochure-btn" href="#">Download Our Brochure</a>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="col-md-4 col-sm-12">\r\n<div class="services-form">\r\n<h3>Schedule a Free Consultation</h3>\r\n[contact-form-7 id="184" title="App form"]\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="col-md-12">\r\n<h3>FAQ</h3>\r\n<div class="toggle">\r\n<div class="toggle-title ">\r\n<h3><i></i><span class="title-name">How does Vanquish work?</span></h3>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="toggle-inner">Vanquish delivers energy to areas of unwanted fat in the form of RADIOFREQUENCY. Radiofrequency is a type of energy that changes the temperature of selected tissues. With Vanquish, the target is fat, not skin, muscle, or other tissues. When the fat hits the targeted temperature, the fat cells are destroyed. Once the fat cells have been destroyed, your body clears them away in a manner similar to the way you clear up a bruise. There is no downtime, no compression garments, and no special instructions you have to follow.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="toggle">\r\n<div class="toggle-title ">\r\n<h3><i></i><span class="title-name">What areas can you treat with Vanquish Therapy?</span></h3>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="toggle-inner">Vanquish was designed to treat the abdomen and muffin top, or love handles. After your consultation, Dr. DeRosa can determine if other areas of your body can be treated.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="toggle">\r\n<div class="toggle-title ">\r\n<h3><i></i><span class="title-name">How many treatments will I need?</span></h3>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="toggle-inner">Most commonly 4 sessions is recommended, lasting about 30 minutes each. These are generally done once a week, but the timing is not critical. Results can be seen as early as one week, and the final results can be seen as soon as 2 weeks after the last treatment. As this is a targeted spot reduction treatment, and not a weight loss system, you still will need to maintain a healthy lifestyle. The fat reduction is permanent, but you still have the ability to gain weight.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="toggle">\r\n<div class="toggle-title ">\r\n<h3><i></i><span class="title-name">Is it safe?</span></h3>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="toggle-inner">Yes! There have been no significant serious side effects reported with the Vanquish treatment except for some pinkness on the treated area that may last for about 15-30 minutes. Patients should drink more water the day of treatment and the day after, and should continue to watch what they eat and exercise to enhance the results. With any procedure it is important to discuss your complete medical history with Dr. DeRosa.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="toggle">\r\n<div class="toggle-title ">\r\n<h3><i></i><span class="title-name">What can I expect after treatment?</span></h3>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="toggle-inner">Following your Vanquish Therapy you may notice some mild redness in the treatment area. This usually disappears within a few hours. You may resume normal activities immediately. Patients should increase water intake and continue to watch what they eat and exercise to maximize cosmetic results.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="toggle">\r\n<div class="toggle-title ">\r\n<h3><i></i><span class="title-name">Who is a candidate for Vanquish?</span></h3>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="toggle-inner">In most cases anyone wishing to reduce fat in a targeted area is a candidate. In your initial consultation, we will discuss with you the proper treatment plan for your body type. If you have an implant such as a pacemaker, cardio converter, cochlear implant, a breast expander or other metal implants you MUST NOT undergo Vanquish treatments. Also, if you are pregnant or nursing, or think you might be pregnant you may NOT undergo Vanquish treatments.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="toggle">\r\n<div class="toggle-title ">\r\n<h3><i></i><span class="title-name">Why choose Vanquish Therapy over other procedures?</span></h3>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="toggle-inner">No surgery\r\nNo downtime\r\nRapid results.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'Vanquish Non-Surgical', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'non-surgical-vanquish', '', '', '2017-12-20 11:21:10', '2017-12-20 11:21:10', '', 0, 'http://webdesigndemo1.com/phr-centers/?post_type=our_services&#038;p=56', 0, 'our_services', '', 0),
