d the newest Laser hair removal machine called the Vectus both have a special contact-cooling hand-piece. It directs the laser energy to the hair root while protecting and cooling the surrounding skin.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<a href="#backto">Back To Question List</a>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>', 'Laser Hair Removal', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '9-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-12-04 10:04:41', '2017-12-04 10:04:41', '', 9, 'http://webdesigndemo1.com/phr-centers/9-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
