(147, 1, '2017-12-15 08:47:11', '2017-12-15 08:47:11', '<div class="row">\n	<div class="col-md-9 col-sm-8">\n<img class="img-right" src="http://webdesigndemo1.com/phr-centers/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/skin.jpg" />As you age your skin loses its elasticity. Harmful UV rays, smoking, alcohol, as well as an imbalanced diet can contribute to the wrinkles and sagging looking skin, the look that appears on your skin when its lost its elasticity and collagen. Although night creams, moisturizers, and microdermabrasion claim to temporarily reduce wrinkles, the only way to get permanent results is through Skin Rejuvenation treatments. PHR Laser Centers offers several solutions for your skin care needs. Call for your skin care consultation.\n\n<strong> Botox/Dysport and Facial Fillers</strong>\n\nBotox and Dysport is a prescription medication that temporarily improves the appearance of moderate to severe frown lines between your brows, on your forehead and around your eyes. Botox and Dysport can also be used for hyperhydrosis (excessive sweating). This procedure is quick and painless with no down-time that will leave you looking refreshed and flawless without the need for invasive surgical procedures.\n\nSoft tissue dermal fillers such as Juvederm, Restylane, Sculptra, Perlane and Radiesse can be injected into wrinkles, furrows, scars and lips. Fillers are a safe, easy and quick way to immediately erase years of aging while improving the appearance of your skin. During your consultation, we will discuss which filler is the best choice to achieve the desired results you are seeking.\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<strong>Custom Chemical Peels</strong>\n\nChemical peels are one of the oldest cosmetic procedures in the world to help you achieve smoother, more beautiful skin. Chemical peels remove the damaged outer layers of the skin and is an effective treatment for acne, uneven skin tone from sun damage and fine lines. PHR CENTERS customizes each peel according to your skin condition as well as the depth of penetration to produce a more beautiful, glowing appearance.\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<strong>Microdermabrasion</strong>\n\nMicrodermabrasion are based on principles of exfoliation. Different from many other chemical exfoliations available today. It is a dry exfoliation method that is safe to use on many parts of the body including the face area. Exfoliating can also be understood as the emoval of the dead skin cells. By using the special crystals we provide, it can help smoothing out wrinkles and fine lines. It is also very beneficial for scars left from wounds or chicken pox. It also helps to unclog pores, stimulate the circulation of the skin, eliminate dead skin cells from the top layer of the skin and improves the skin ability to retain moisture. Giving the skin a more youthful and healthy appearance.\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<strong>IPL for Skin Rejuvenation</strong>\n\nIPL is a laser that can be customized to each patients needs and concerns. Dark spots on hands, face, neck and chest are the most popular areas. Since it requires minimal recovery time, it is a perfect solution for those who want to reverse the signs of aging, giving you back the skin you deserve.', 'Skin Rejuvenation', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '54-autosave-v1', '', '', '2017-12-15 08:47:11', '2017-12-15 08:47:11', '', 54, 'http://webdesigndemo1.com/phr-centers/54-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
